## üåç Regional & Cultural Preferences

### **Location:** Doha, Qatar

### **Measurement Systems**
- ‚è∞ **Time:** 24-hour clock system
- ‚öñÔ∏è **Weight:** Grams (g) and kilograms (kg)
- üìè **Distance/Volume:** Metric system

### **Dietary Restrictions (Qatar-specific)**
- ‚ùå **Pork products are NOT available** in Qatar (not permitted by law)
- All meal planning must exclude pork and pork-based products

### **Meal Style Preferences**
- **Breakfast:** Savoury/savory items preferred for family meals
- **Snacks:** Sweet items acceptable for children (Nicholas & Gabriel)
- **Menu Format:** All meal plans should be presented in **table format**
- **Cooking Style:** European-style meals and cooking preferred

